photo_memories.feelings: The venue is at Y Combinator, the most famous startup accelerator in the world.
Excited to start the hackathon! We are going to build something amazing!
Deep in coding mode. The initial prototype is taking shape nicely.
When I'm exhausted, I walked around and saw hackers grinding on their projects. It was inspiring to see their passion and dedication.
At the venue, it was fun to see photos from great moments at YC. It was a great reminder that we are not alone in this journey.
Final demo time. Everyone built something amazing
